Title: La distribución del ingreso: un breve resúmen de tres décadas
Abstract: This paper summarizes the main results on changes in poverty and inequality in Argentina and the world in the last three decades, and discusses the progresses made by the Economics field in that period toward a better understanding of the distributional issues. 
